Citation.sTitle: Excess Enthalpies of Binary Mixtures of 1-Hexene with Some n-Alkanes at 298.15 K
Citation.sAbstract: Excess molar enthalpies, measured at 298.15 K in a flow microcalorimeter, are reported for mixtures of 1-hexene with n-heptane, n-octane, n-decane, n-dodecane and n-tetradecane. Smooth Redlich-Kister representations of the results are described. It was found that the Liebermann-Fried model also provided good representations of the data.
